'''Octogenarian''' is an [[Achievements|achievement]] of the Longevity section. The player can earn this achievement by living till the age of 80.

== Trivia ==
* If the player doesn't get in trouble too much and mantains good [[stats]], this achievement is easy to obtain.
* This achievement isn't directly connected to any [[ribbon]], so obtaining it doesn't guarantee a certain ribbon.
